ld packages are used. I found documentation for the 2 alpha versions using `tools.jackson`, so I'll provide guidance to adopt the Jackson 3 package while avoiding Jackson 2.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating workflow and dependencies**\\n\\nI'm considering how to help streamline the workflow. There's a risk because existing tests from version 1.6.2 may fail due to a package rename. Adding Jackson 2 won’t satisfy methods that use Jackson 3’s JsonNode. If I summarize that no extra dependencies are needed, I’ll also mention that tests must be migrated to Jackson 3 imports. I should include deterministic setups and ensure everything is JSON-only, without any markdown. I need that \\\"agent_guidance\\\" string as well.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"No extra Maven dependency, Docker image, environment variable, or system property is needed; jackson-jq 2.0.0-alpha1 already brings Jackson 3 databind transitively, but tests must use the Jackson 3 API packages.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"When updating or generating tests for net.thisptr:jackson-jq:2.0.0-alpha1, use Jackson 3 imports such as tools.jackson.databind.JsonNode and tools.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper. Do not keep the 1.6.2-era com.fasterxml.jackson.databind imports or add Jackson 2 databind just to satisfy them; jackson-jq 2.0.0-alpha1 method signatures accept tools.jackson.databind.JsonNode.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Copying the existing 1.6.2 test unchanged will fail javac because com.fasterxml.jackson.databind is no longer on the compile classpath for the tested 2.0.0-alpha1 setup.\",\n    \"Adding com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind would mask the import error but would not match jackson-jq 2.0.0-alpha1 APIs, which are typed against tools.jackson.databind.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02eb2df77dc5d7a5016a402cddab08819589cf0dbf47bfc560\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 518, "output": 974, "cacheRead": 28672, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30164, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782590675307, "responseId": "resp_02eb2df77dc5d7a5016a402cd3c71481958439bfa63ea18bb2"}}
